{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Wordpress Installing","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"BeoNews Pro - React Native mobile app for Wordpress","meta_description":"BeoNews is an app that does magic for your website by converting your Wordpress website into mobile true native app with customized contents within a fillip.","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"beonews","toc":null,"keywords":["beonews","beonews pro magento","wordpress app","react-native","react-native app"]},"html":"<p>This section will help you walk through the minimum required setup to run the project.</p>\n<p>For easy to config the Wordpress site, you can download the site from <a href=\"http://github.com/inspireui/mstorethis\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://github.com/inspireui/mstore</a>, this was already config and install all plugin that use for the app, or if you have your existing website, you can following by below setting.</p>\n<h2 id=\"wordpres-plugins-install\"><a href=\"#wordpres-plugins-install\" aria-label=\"wordpres plugins install permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Wordpres Plugins install</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>JSON API</strong>: A RESTful API for WordPress, this plugin is used for only the registration feature (other request from the API we use default REST API from Wordpress site)</li>\n<li><strong>JSON API User:</strong> Extends the JSON API for RESTful user registration, authentication, password reset...</li>\n<li><strong>Better Rest API Featured Image</strong>: for some reason the image is not populate correctly so that need to install this plugin to support to show the image.</li>\n<li><strong>OneSignal Push Notifications</strong> (optional)<strong>:</strong> push notify to the mobile app, or web using OneSignal dashboard admin. This feature is support on Pro version.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"download-links\"><a href=\"#download-links\" aria-label=\"download links permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Download links:</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/json-api/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://wordpress.org/plugins/json-api/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/json-api-user/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://wordpress.org/plugins/json-api-user/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/better-rest-api-featured-images/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://wordpress.org/plugins/better-rest-api-featured-images/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/onesignal-free-web-push-notifications/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-rest-api-cache/</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"enable-worpdress-setting\"><a href=\"#enable-worpdress-setting\" aria-label=\"enable worpdress setting permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Enable Worpdress setting</h2>\n<h3 id=\"permalink-url-setting\"><a href=\"#permalink-url-setting\" aria-label=\"permalink url setting permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Permalink URL setting</strong>:</h3>\n<p>Go to <strong>Common Setting</strong>, change the URL to <strong>Post name</strong>, this is required for the setting otherwise some images could not loading.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/9bf021a5a52894127b6ccf0ba6c3b8e2/0e202/beonew-20.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 32.89569657184537%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"beonew 20\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9bf021a5a52894127b6ccf0ba6c3b8e2/efcfb/beonew-20.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9bf021a5a52894127b6ccf0ba6c3b8e2/11053/beonew-20.png 200w,\n/static/9bf021a5a52894127b6ccf0ba6c3b8e2/1b42c/beonew-20.png 400w,\n/static/9bf021a5a52894127b6ccf0ba6c3b8e2/efcfb/beonew-20.png 800w,\n/static/9bf021a5a52894127b6ccf0ba6c3b8e2/d25cb/beonew-20.png 1200w,\n/static/9bf021a5a52894127b6ccf0ba6c3b8e2/22e61/beonew-20.png 1600w,\n/static/9bf021a5a52894127b6ccf0ba6c3b8e2/4b363/beonew-20.png 2400w,\n/static/9bf021a5a52894127b6ccf0ba6c3b8e2/0e202/beonew-20.png 2742w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3 id=\"membership-registration\"><a href=\"#membership-registration\" aria-label=\"membership registration permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a><strong>Membership registration</strong>:</h3>\n<p>Enable the option <strong>Anyone</strong> can register.</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/997c52d35bef5b2d056ee2ec61efee02/09449/beonew-22.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 18.759124087591243%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"beonew 22\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/997c52d35bef5b2d056ee2ec61efee02/efcfb/beonew-22.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/997c52d35bef5b2d056ee2ec61efee02/11053/beonew-22.png 200w,\n/static/997c52d35bef5b2d056ee2ec61efee02/1b42c/beonew-22.png 400w,\n/static/997c52d35bef5b2d056ee2ec61efee02/efcfb/beonew-22.png 800w,\n/static/997c52d35bef5b2d056ee2ec61efee02/d25cb/beonew-22.png 1200w,\n/static/997c52d35bef5b2d056ee2ec61efee02/22e61/beonew-22.png 1600w,\n/static/997c52d35bef5b2d056ee2ec61efee02/4b363/beonew-22.png 2400w,\n/static/997c52d35bef5b2d056ee2ec61efee02/09449/beonew-22.png 2740w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h3 id=\"enable-post-a-comment\"><a href=\"#enable-post-a-comment\" aria-label=\"enable post a comment permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Enable Post a comment</h3>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b550ff27ef239cad4c65ed8bdba089fc/46dc3/beonew-21.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 13.956466069142126%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"beonew 21\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/b550ff27ef239cad4c65ed8bdba089fc/efcfb/beonew-21.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b550ff27ef239cad4c65ed8bdba089fc/11053/beonew-21.png 200w,\n/static/b550ff27ef239cad4c65ed8bdba089fc/1b42c/beonew-21.png 400w,\n/static/b550ff27ef239cad4c65ed8bdba089fc/efcfb/beonew-21.png 800w,\n/static/b550ff27ef239cad4c65ed8bdba089fc/d25cb/beonew-21.png 1200w,\n/static/b550ff27ef239cad4c65ed8bdba089fc/46dc3/beonew-21.png 1562w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>And from the <code class=\"language-text\">functions.php</code> file (this could be added as the child function from your template) add  following code:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"php\"><pre class=\"language-php\"><code class=\"language-php\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">filter_rest_allow_anonymous_comments</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token boolean constant\">true</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">add_filter</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'rest_allow_anonymous_comments'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token single-quoted-string string\">'filter_rest_allow_anonymous_comments'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"app-config\"><a href=\"#app-config\" aria-label=\"app config permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>App config</h2>\n<p>Go the project folder, open the file: <strong>src/common/appConfig.json</strong> and follow 2 simple steps to setup the app:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Step 1: Change your Wordpress site URL</li>\n<li>Step 2: Config the home UI layout </li>\n</ul>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d991ab4c9f36c69e5658f69d2accae4a/23b92/config.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 57.64611689351481%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"config\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d991ab4c9f36c69e5658f69d2accae4a/efcfb/config.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d991ab4c9f36c69e5658f69d2accae4a/11053/config.png 200w,\n/static/d991ab4c9f36c69e5658f69d2accae4a/1b42c/config.png 400w,\n/static/d991ab4c9f36c69e5658f69d2accae4a/efcfb/config.png 800w,\n/static/d991ab4c9f36c69e5658f69d2accae4a/d25cb/config.png 1200w,\n/static/d991ab4c9f36c69e5658f69d2accae4a/22e61/config.png 1600w,\n/static/d991ab4c9f36c69e5658f69d2accae4a/4b363/config.png 2400w,\n/static/d991ab4c9f36c69e5658f69d2accae4a/23b92/config.png 2498w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>It's possible to update this step via the Cebuilder tools, at Customization tab</p>\n</blockquote>","fields":{"slug":"/beonews/wordpress-setting/"},"timeToRead":2,"excerpt":"This section will help you walk through the minimum required setup to run the project. For easy to config the Wordpress site, you canâ€¦","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/minhpham/Data/Projects/inspireui-documents/docs/content/beonews/wordpress-setting.md"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/beonews/wordpress-setting/"}}